entity.description: Created in 1997 by veteran journalist Barbara Walters, "The View" is a daytime talk show hosted by women -- including Whoopi Goldberg, Joy Behar, Sunny Hostin, Sara Haines, Alyssa Farah Griffin and Ana Navarro -- and each offers her take on the day's news during the opening "Hot Topics" segment. Later, the ladies welcome various celebrities, who join them in a chat or perform for the audience. The program also offers tips on beauty, fashion, diet and relationships. Known for their freewheeling style, the hosts are often lampooned in late-night sketches.

text:
6/ So how do we know if #bitcoin will be a bubble or will be one of the best investments of all time? We don't. Time + the market is the ultimate truth teller and will never lie, place your bets. No-coiners stay short, HODLers buy dips.

But no, #bitcoin is not a bubble 🙂

5/ When people claim #bitcoin is a bubble in real time not only are they voicing an arguably false statement, but they're also claiming to have extremely deep #bitcoin/market knowledge such as the true value of a new asset going through price discovery in its infant years

4/ If #bitcoin falls to $0 because of some technical flaw, we can look back and declare it a bubble. If #bitcoin turns out to be a new sound money digital asset and becomes the worlds reserve currency (or whatever) then bulls will be validated by the market.

3/ Think #bitcoin is currently overvalued? Short it. But a rise in price and 1,000s of % increase in year-over-year change simply validates bulls. It does not validate your “wow, look how far down the fall to $0 is” statement. https://t.co/3YdFduB2Ju

1/ Quick thoughts on people calling #bitcoin a bubble:

It is a bit absurd and laughable that people/"analysts" can declare #bitcoin a bubble in real time. A bubble is declared in _hindsight_, ridiculous to declare one before the devastating crash.
@mBTCPizpie trust #bitcoin as long as you can HODL it

@bennd77 ♥️

much love my friend I appreciate you! i’ll be back in no time, nothing can keep me from #bitcoin 😃

Those involved know that the #bitcoin community treats one and other like family.

I’ll never forget regaining consciousness in my hospital bed and scrolling through twitter and seeing your tweets.

Sorry for the emotion but I really do love you all, thank you. 

#⚡️ #🌚 https://t.co/FmHtPzrkMe
